data.description: Beautiful Birch Model featuring finished walk out basement, deck w gas grill hook up, with spectacular views, one car attached garage.  Entrance foyer leads to open space Living Room w fireplace Dining room with 9' ceilings and views of the country- side. 1st floor has hardwood floors, custom molding package including 3-piece crown, chair rail, wains coating and recessed lighting. The kitchen has dishwasher, gas range self-cleaning oven. Powder room on first floor. The second-floor master bedroom has a cathedral ceiling, 3 large windows, large walk-in closet and master bath with soaking tub, separate stall shower, and double vanity.  Bedrooms 2 & 3 are ample size with double closets, the main bath has shower over tub and the second-floor laundry provides convenience.  2nd floor has upgraded carpet in bedrooms and hardwood in hallway. The lower-level family room measures 24x23 with lots of light 3 large windows, walk out slider, spectacular views. All of the amenities that go with Panther Valley; 24-hour security gate, 3 pools, basketball & tennis courts, hiking trails, scenic overlook, bus to NYC w free parking at Panther Valley Mall. Rt 80 is minutes away.
